The paper focuses on a replanning method for quadrotors, which falls under the field of robotics (cs.RO). The proposed method involves optimization techniques (cs.AI), as well as path planning and navigation in 3-D environments (cs.CV, cs.SY). The paper also mentions benchmark evaluation and comparison with state-of-the-art methods (cs.LG).
